download_gpkg           Download geopackage to tempdir
download_metadata       Support function to download metadata
                        internally used in geobr
geobr                   'geobr' package
grid_state_correspondence_table
                        A correspondence table indicating what
                        quadrants of IBGE's statistical grid intersect
                        with each Brazilian state
list_geobr              List all datasets available in the geobr
                        package
load_gpkg               Load geopackage from tempdir to global
                        environment
lookup_muni             Lookup municipality codes and names
read_amazon             Download official data of Brazil's Legal Amazon
                        as an sf object.
read_biomes             Download official data of Brazilian biomes as
                        an sf object.
read_census_tract       Download shape files of census tracts of the
                        Brazilian Population Census (Only years 2000
                        and 2010 are currently available).
read_conservation_units
                        Download official data of Brazilian
                        conservation untis as an sf object.
read_country            Download shape file of Brazil as sf objects.
                        Data at scale 1:250,000, using Geodetic
                        reference system "SIRGAS2000" and CRS(4674)
read_disaster_risk_area
                        Download official data of disaster risk areas
                        as an sf object.
read_health_facilities
                        Download geolocated data of health facilities
                        as an sf object.
read_immediate_region   Download shape files of Brazil's Immediate
                        Geographic Areas as sf objects
read_indigenous_land    Download official data of indigenous lands as
                        an sf object.
read_intermediate_region
                        Download shape files of Brazil's Intermediate
                        Geographic Areas as sf objects.
read_meso_region        Download shape files of meso region as sf
                        objects. Data at scale 1:250,000, using
                        Geodetic reference system "SIRGAS2000" and
                        CRS(4674)
read_metro_area         Download shape files of official metropolitan
                        areas in Brazil as an sf object.
read_micro_region       Download shape files of micro region as sf
                        objects
read_municipal_seat     Download official data of municipal seats (sede
                        dos municipios) in Brazil as an sf object.
read_municipality       Download shape files of Brazilian
                        municipalities as sf objects.
read_region             Download shape file of Brazil Regions as sf
                        objects.
read_semiarid           Download official data of Brazilian Semiarid as
                        an sf object.
read_state              Download shapefiles of Brazilian states as sf
                        objects.
read_statistical_grid   Download shape files of IBGE's statistical grid
                        (200 x 200 meters) as sf objects. Data at scale
                        1:250,000, using Geodetic reference system
                        "SIRGAS2000" and CRS(4674)
read_urban_area         Download official data of urbanized areas in
                        Brazil as an sf object.
read_weighting_area     Download shape files of Census Weighting Areas
                        (area de ponderacao) of the Brazilian
                        Population Census.
select_data_type        Select data type: 'original' or 'simplified'
                        (default)
select_metadata         Select metadata
select_year_input       Select year input
